  "prompt": "Which is the best training institute for spoken English in Pune?",
  "response": "Choosing the best training institute for spoken English in Pune can depend on various factors such as your personal learning style, location, budget, and specific needs. However, here are some highly recommended institutes in Pune that are known for their quality in teaching spoken English:\n\n1. **British Council Pune**:\n   - The British Council is renowned worldwide for its English language programs. They offer a variety of courses tailored to different proficiency levels, with experienced trainers and modern facilities.\n\n2. **Wadhwani Institute of English**:\n   - This institute focuses on practical communication skills and offers courses that are designed to improve spoken English in real-life situations. They have a good reputation for their methodology and results.\n\n3. **Veta Spoken English**:\n   - Veta is another well-regarded institute in Pune with a focus on improving spoken English through interactive and engaging methods. They have multiple centers across the city.\n\n4. **Inlingua Pune**:\n   - Inlingua offers personalized training programs in spoken English. They are known for their international curriculum and experienced faculty.\n\n5. **Enguru Spoken English Classes**:\n   - Enguru offers comprehensive courses for all levels and is known for its student-centric approach and flexible timings.\n\nIt's a good idea to visit the websites of these institutes, read reviews, and possibly attend demo classes to see which one suits your needs best. Additionally, consider factors such as class size, course duration, and the qualifications of the trainers when making your decision.",
